---
description: Government platform business constraints
globs: ["src/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

# Permissions

Never:

- Hardcode permissions
- Hardcode roles

Always:

- Read permissions from API
- Use permission guards
- Hide unauthorized actions

# Bilingual Support

All user-facing text must support:

- English
- Hindi

Never hardcode display strings.

Use translation keys.

# Auditability

Actions that change data should support:

- user tracking
- timestamps
- audit logs

# Data Integrity

Never trust frontend validation alone.

Backend remains source of truth.

# Government Platform Standards

Prioritize:

- reliability
- accessibility
- maintainability
- security

over visual effects or clever implementations.